text: The 1973 World Table Tennis Championships – Women's Singles was the 32nd edition of the women's singles championship. Hu Yu Lan defeated Alice Grófová in the final by three sets to nil, to win the title. ==Results== ==See also== List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== \- Category:1973 in women's table tennis
title: 1973 World Table Tennis Championships – Women's Singles
